<lb ed="I" n="0050a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 19</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0050a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>錡雙胡廿人等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0052a" xml:id="I01.0019.0052a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0052a00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0052a0101">富平令王承祖　但官錡眾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">舉</unclear>　平望田安周　邑子錡陽生
<lb ed="I" n="0052a02"/>　　　　　　　侍者錡石珍　平望錡神裕　邑子錡景略
<lb ed="I" n="0052a03"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　但官錡思山　邑子錡神歡
<lb ed="I" n="0052a04"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　邑正錡平洛　邑子錡虎略
<lb ed="I" n="0052a05"/>邑師錡雙胡　　侍者錡舉　　邑正王買興</p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0052b" xml:id="I01.0019.0052b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0052b00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陰</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0052b0101">典坐錡道憘
<lb ed="I" n="0052b02"/>典錄錡承祖　邑子錡馬仁
<lb ed="I" n="0052b03"/>邑子錡申起　香火錡神敬
<lb ed="I" n="0052b04"/>典錄錡歡洛</p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0052c" xml:id="I01.0019.0052c" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0052c00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之三　碑側</cb:mulu><head>之三　碑側</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052c01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0052c0101">□□□□□先<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052001" n="0052001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052001" n="0052001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052001" n="0052001"/>劫<anchor xml:id="end0052001"/>以<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052002" n="0052002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052002" n="0052002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052002" n="0052002"/>來<anchor xml:id="end0052002"/>。應形化世。靜志靈<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052003" n="0052003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052003" n="0052003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052003" n="0052003"/>淵<anchor xml:id="end0052003"/>。清脩万行。乃運窮通。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">濁</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">明</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0052c02"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">三</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">世</unclear>之常。事<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052004" n="0052004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052004" n="0052004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052004" n="0052004"/>體<anchor xml:id="end0052004"/>真極之妙。嘗獲无為以自安。控玄範以騰覩。馳<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">逸</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0052c03"/>万□。人天蒙<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052005" n="0052005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052005" n="0052005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052005" n="0052005"/>慶<anchor xml:id="end0052005"/>。感緣既周。凝神靜<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052006" n="0052006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052006" n="0052006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052006" n="0052006"/>樂<anchor xml:id="end0052006"/>。真容雖遷。像化<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052007" n="0052007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052007" n="0052007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052007" n="0052007"/>彌<anchor xml:id="end0052007"/>振。然今千載之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">下</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0052c04"/>合邑廿人等。覺世非常。捨己名珍。為國為家。造石像一軀。彫<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052008" n="0052008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052008" n="0052008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052008" n="0052008"/>剋<anchor xml:id="end0052008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052009" n="0052009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052009" n="0052009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052009" n="0052009"/>成<anchor xml:id="end0052009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052010" n="0052010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052010" n="0052010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052010" n="0052010"/>就<anchor xml:id="end0052010"/>。寫真
<lb ed="I" n="0052c05"/>容<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052011" n="0052011"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052011" n="0052011"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052011" n="0052011"/>止<anchor xml:id="end0052011"/>。應安處路衝。高平<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052012" n="0052012"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052012" n="0052012"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052012" n="0052012"/>顯<anchor xml:id="end0052012"/>唱。討邑恭養。隨時不闕。以是造像功德。上願皇
<lb ed="I" n="0052c06"/>□陛下紹隆万劫。匡<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">拯</unclear>三寶。千載不隧。下願合邑亡過師尊父母。長志天
<lb ed="I" n="0052c07"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">闕</unclear>。託化紫蓮。栖神万法。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052013" n="0052013"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052013" n="0052013"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052013" n="0052013"/>逮<anchor xml:id="end0052013"/>及合邑。三界六趣。咸同斯<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>慶<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052014" n="0052014"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052014" n="0052014"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052014" n="0052014"/>業<anchor xml:id="end0052014"/><anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>成<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>真道。
<lb ed="I" n="0052c08"/>大□神龜三年歲次庚子年四月甲辰<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0052015" n="0052015"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0052015" n="0052015"/><anchor xml:id="beg0052015" n="0052015"/>朔<anchor xml:id="end0052015"/>八日造訖。</p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0052d" xml:id="I01.0019.0052d" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0052d00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之四　碑側</cb:mulu><head>之四　碑側</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052d01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0052d0101">邑子錡黑奴
<lb ed="I" n="0052d02"/>邑子錡荊周</p></cb:div></cb:div>
</body>
